Treasure Entertainment is an U.S. based film and media company engaged in the production of feature films, television, music videos, commercials, documentaries and new media. The company also works in new growth areas such as content acquisitions and home media distribution. Treasure Entertainment has three divisions: Feature Films & Television, Music Video & Commercial, and Acquisitions & Distribution.
Treasure Entertainment was founded in August 2000 by Mark Heidelberger and Jesse Felsot.
